    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><style>[data-colorid=bzwcfegdpf]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bzwcfegdpf]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=jzyx5y503k]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jzyx5y503k]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=r8f87w1u68]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=r8f87w1u68]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=o1qfmcpqfr]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=o1qfmcpqfr]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=mtz5fgqrl5]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mtz5fgqrl5]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=zbuqo61cd5]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=zbuqo61cd5]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=f9kshp2d5p]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=f9kshp2d5p]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=zxq097y5i0]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=zxq097y5i0]{color:#cccccc}[data-colorid=p34vkbvcf6]{color:#333333} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=p34vkbvcf6]{color:#cccccc}</style><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> Holdouts are used to collect the CG objects' shadow and reflection that match very closely to the shadow and reflection in the live action plate. You can create a holdout (even without all the RenderMan parameters applied) by choosing the Holdout shelf button with your desired holdout objects selected and your ROP node. We will add the appropriate RenderMan Holdout Attribute&nbsp;and set it to &quot;on&quot; as well as setup the correct displays and filters to generate a shadow result for compositing. </span><br /></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> </span><br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645461/rfh_holdoutShelfSelect.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141679&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645461/rfh_holdoutShelfSelect.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141679&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"37\" data-width=\"192\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645485\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_holdoutShelfSelect.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f90aa721-4c4f-4f63-8cb8-afd9126789e5\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> </span><br /></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">To make an object as a holdout, simply check&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> </span></strong><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661827\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Holdout</span></strong></a><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> </span></strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">in the geometry's </span><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">RenderMan | Trace</span></strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> Tab or use the </span><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Shelf Button</span></strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">.</span><br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"612\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/holdout.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141679&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=259\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645461/holdout.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141679&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"276\" data-width=\"652\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645482\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdout.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ff16e9b3-af2e-4390-90b5-7d4a014ab82a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/holdout.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141679&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=652&amp;height=276 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/holdout.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141679&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=259 1x\" /></span><p>Your fully shaded objects will now catch shadows and render environmental effects like indirect diffuse light and reflections. This allows you to integrate CG objects into a filmed or live action plate by catching the shadows and effects of the CG object onto holdout geometry made to look like the filmed environment.</p><p /><p>You will need to setup the correct outputs and displays after choosing your holdout objects.</p><ul><li><p><span data-colorid=\"f9kshp2d5p\"> occluded, unoccluded, shadow AOVs should be added to display, these require the corresponding LPE. Below are three </span><em><span data-colorid=\"r8f87w1u68\">color</span></em><span data-colorid=\"bzwcfegdpf\"> LPE preceded by their name.</span><br /><span data-colorid=\"p34vkbvcf6\"> </span></p><p><code>shadow</code> <br /><code>occluded&nbsp;</code> <code>l</code> <code>pe:holdouts;C[DS]+[LO]</code> <br /><code>unoccluded&nbsp;</code> <code>lpe:holdouts;unoccluded;C[DS]+[LO]</code><br />\n        <br />\n        <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"420\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/rfh_HoldoutLPE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141907&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=420&amp;height=362\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645461/rfh_HoldoutLPE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141907&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645491\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_HoldoutLPE.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"992680a1-7b3d-49ea-877f-87e615554e94\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/rfh_HoldoutLPE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141907&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=830&amp;height=716 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/rfh_HoldoutLPE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141907&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=420&amp;height=362 1x\" /></span>\n        <br />\n        <br />\n      </p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662371\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrShadowDisplayFilter</a> vop must be created and added to ROP as display filter (in Advanced Tab)</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"442\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/rfh_HoldoutDisplayFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141906&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=145\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645461/rfh_HoldoutDisplayFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141906&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"267\" data-width=\"810\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645488\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_HoldoutDisplayFilter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cd6f9efd-2c00-4bfd-b19a-86bf700d0b3a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/rfh_HoldoutDisplayFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141906&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=810&amp;height=267 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645461/rfh_HoldoutDisplayFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433141906&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=145 1x\" /></span></li><li><p><span data-colorid=\"o1qfmcpqfr\">The AOV parameters on the display filter should reference the AOV names created above</span></p></li></ul><p><span data-colorid=\"zxq097y5i0\"> </span><br /></p><p><span data-colorid=\"mtz5fgqrl5\">To preview this effect while interactively rendering, you could make use of an additional display filter after the shadow display filter:&nbsp; </span><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661891\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span data-colorid=\"zbuqo61cd5\">PxrImageDisplayFilter</span></a><span data-colorid=\"jzyx5y503k\">  </span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> </span><br /></p><p />"
    }
  },
